20coach%20Stephen%20Fleming%20revealed%20the%20reason%20for%20keeping%20MS%20Dhoni%20stationed%20in%20the%20final%20three%20overs%20instead%20of%20promoting%20him%20up%20in%20the%20batting%20order%20following%20his%20cameo%20against%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024.%20After%20being%20put%20to%20bat%2C%20Dhoni%20arrived%20on%20the%20crease%20with%20two%20overs%20left%20and%20CSK%20reduced%20to%20142%2F6.%20In%20the%20next%2012%20deliveries%2C%20Dhoni%20recreated%20the%20magic%20at%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20against%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20and%20effortlessly%20raced%20to%2028%20runs%20in%20a%20mere%20nine%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni's%20performance%20in%20the%20IPL%20has%20led%20to%20fans%20asking%20for%20a%20promotion%20of%20the%20former%20CSK%20skipper%20in%20the%20batting%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Fleming%20revealed%20that%20Dhoni%20is%20still%20recovering%20from%20knee%20issues%20for%20which%20he%20underwent%20surgery%20after%20the%20conclusion%20of%20last%20year's%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20inspirational%2C%20his%20batting%20this%20season%2C%20even%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20has%20been%20very%20crisp%20and%20the%20team%20is%20not%20surprised%20to%20see%20what%20he%20is%20doing.%20His%20skill%20level%20during%20the%20pre-season%20was%20very%20high.%20Other%20years%20he%20had%20a%20problem%20with%20his%20knee%20and%20he%20is%20still%20recovering%2C%20which%20is%20why%20there%20are%20only%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20balls%20he%20can%20function%20well.%20I%20think%20everyone%20wants%20to%20see%20him%20for%20longer%20as%20we%20do%20but%20that%20amount%20of%20time%20is%20right%3B%20we%20need%20him%20for%20the%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleming%20said%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LSG%20pace%20duo%20of%20Yash%20Thakur%20and%20Mohsin%20Khan%20were%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20as%20Dhoni%20made%20the%20wave%20of%20yellow%20erupt%20in%20the%20stands%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20two%20towering%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20erupted%20and%20applauded%20each%20shot%20that%20came%20off%20Dhoni's%20bat%2C%20which%20took%20CSK%20to%20a%20competitive%20total%20of%20176%2F6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%202-3%20over%20cameo%2C%20he%20is%20owning%20that%20space%2C%20it%20is%20up%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20batting%20unit%20to%20get%20us%20sort%20of%20in%20a%20good%20position%20where%20he%20can%20push%20us%20over%20the%20top%20and%20he%20is%20doing%20that%20pretty%20much%20every%20time%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20which%20is%20great%20to%20watch%20and%20what%20an%20amazing%20atmosphere%20when%20he%20comes%20out%20and%20entertains.%20We%20are%20incredibly%20proud%20of%20what%20he%20has%20achieved%20and%20we%20marvel%20at%20the%20amount%20of%20love%20that%20he%20gets.%20We%20are%20incredibly%20proud%20that%20he%20is%20part%20of%20our%20side%20and%20he%20is%20pretty%20much%20the%20heartbeat%20of%20our%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleming%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecapping%20the%20match%2C%20Dhoni's%20cameo%2C%20combined%20with%20Ravindra%20Jadeja's%20unbeaten%2057%2C%20propelled%20CSK%20to%20176%2F6.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reply%2C%20skipper%20KL%20Rahul%20and%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20forged%20a%20134-run%20opening%20stand%2C%20which%20ensured%20the%20hosts%20walked%20away%20with%20an%208-wicket%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713585120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6643ia7g_ms-dhoni-afp_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fproblem-with-knee-he-is-still-csk-coach-on-ms-dhonis-limited-batting-in-ipl-2024-5482088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni%20arrived%20on%20the%20crease%20with%20two%20overs%20left%20and%20CSK%20reduced%20t