%2Findia-news%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk-postpones-india-visit-new-dates-yet-to-be-announced-124042000099_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20India%20Trip%20May%20See%20Breakthroughs%20For%20Starlink%2C%20Tesla%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20Tesla%20Inc.'s%20largest-ever%20round%20of%20layoffs%20and%20hours%20before%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20will%20fly%20to%20India%20to%20squeeze%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20It's%20not%20an%20idle%20period%20for%20PM%20Modi%20either%2C%20who's%20criss-crossing%20states%20for%20election%20rallies%20days%20after%20voting%20kicked%20off%20in%20the%20world's%20biggest%20election%20where%20he's%20seeking%20a%20third%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tight%20timing%20of%20their%20meeting%20early%20next%20week%20underscores%20the%20high%20stakes%20for%20both%20men.%20For%20Musk%2C%20the%20prize%20is%20India's%20permission%20for%20SpaceX's%20Starlink%20Inc.%20to%20operate%20in%20what%20will%20be%20by%20far%20its%20biggest%20market%2C%20given%20China's%20resistance%20to%20the%20American%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20PM%20Modi%2C%20the%20appearance%20of%20Tesla%20cars%20in%20the%20streets%20of%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20-%20and%20a%20potential%20investment%20in%20manufacturing%20by%20the%20carmaker%20-%20will%20cast%20him%20as%20a%20leader%20who's%20brought%20marquee%20foreign%20investment%20to%20India%2C%20modernized%20its%20cities%20into%20global%20metropolises%2C%20and%20created%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20symbolic%20of%20the%20growing%20foreign%20investor%20interest%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sonal%20Varma%2C%20chief%20economist%20for%20India%20and%20Asia%20ex-Japan%20at%20Nomura%20Holdings%20Inc.%20This%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20just%20due%20to%20supply%20chain%20diversification%20from%20China%20for%20export%20purposes%2C%20but%20also%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20India's%20burgeoning%20domestic%20demand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trip%20is%20likely%20to%20yield%20breakthroughs%20on%20both%20matters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20has%20already%20received%20assurances%20from%20the%20government%20that%20it%20will%20be%20able%20to%20start%20operating%20in%20the%20country%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20information%20is%20not%20public%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20end%20a%20years-long%20impasse%20with%20the%20Modi%20administration%20and%20help%20Starlink%20close%20in%20on%20two%20homegrown%20rivals%20that%20secured%20India%20licenses%20for%20satellite-based%20internet%20services%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Ministry%20of%20Communications%20didn't%20respond%20to%20an%20email%20seeking%20comment.%20Starlink%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sizable%20investment%20by%20Tesla%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20will%20allow%20Musk%20to%20tap%20India's%20booming%20electric%20vehicle%20market%20and%20counter%20slowing%20demand%20for%20EVs%20elsewhere%20-%20a%20positive%20spin%20for%20the%20carmaker%20when%20Musk%20speaks%20on%20the%20crucial%20earnings%20call%20Tuesday.%20Tesla%20watchers%2C%20however%2C%20will%20want%20to%20see%20action%20on%20the%20ground%20after%20witnessing%20delays%20in%20previously%20announced%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20massive%20Mexico%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20break%20into%20India%20for%20years%20but%20high%20import%20taxes%20were%20a%20deterrent%2C%20something%20Musk%20has%20pointed%20out%20repeatedly.%20India%20last%20month%20lowered%20import%20taxes%20on%20EVs%20from%20foreign%20carmakers%20that%20pledge%20to%20invest%20at%20least%2041.5%20billion%20rupees%20(%24497%20million)%20and%20start%20EV%20production%20from%20a%20local%20factory%20within%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EFrosty%20China%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Starlink's%20services%20are%20available%20in%20the%20US%2C%20much%20of%20Europe%20and%20Asian%20countries%20such%20as%20Japan%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20the%20Philippines%2C%20India%20and%20China%20haven't%20approved%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Tesla%20being%20a%20big%20investor%20in%20China%20and%20Musk%20meeting%20top%20officials%20in%20Beijing%20and%20Shanghai%20during%20a%20visit%20last%20May%20and%20June%2C%20the%20Chinese%20government%20has%20called%20the%20SpaceX%20service%20an%20arm%20of%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20winning%20over%20India%20-%20the%20only%20other%20giant%20market%20with%20a%20billion-plus%20population%20-%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20operations%20would%20also%20mark%20a%20further%20deepening%20of%20the%20security%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20Alex%20Capri%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20for%20the%20Singapore-based%20Hinrich%20Foundation.%20The%20two%20countries%2C%20along%20with%20Japan%20and%20Australia%2C%20are%20cooperating%20in%20the%20Quad%2C%20a%20Washington%20DC-led%20effort%20to%20counter%20China's%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20India%20%26quot%3Bare%20stepping%20up%20surveillance%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BStarlink%20definitely%20has%20a%20role%20in%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ECheckered%20Past%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%2C%20however%2C%20has%20had%20a%20checkered%20past%20with%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20it%20suffered%20a%20setback%20when%20the%20Indian%20government%20asked%20Starlink%20to%20stop%20selling%20subscriptions%20to%20the%20public%20before%20it%20had%20even%20applied%20for%20a%20license.%20The%20administration%20also%20asked%20it%20to%20refund%20the%20subscription%20fees%20collected%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Musk's%20space%20business%20in%20India%20has%20been%20in%20limbo%2C%20stymied%20in%20part%20by%20a%20requirement%20that%20providers%20of%20telecom%20services%20have%20some%20local%20ownership.%20Musk%20has%20resisted%20similar%20rules%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20South%20Africa%20and%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20signs%20of%20a%20thaw%20came%20when%20Modi's%20government%20introduced%20last%20year%20a%20bill%20that%20proposed%20to%20eliminate%20auctions%20for%20allocating%20spectrum%20to%20companies%20that%20offer%20satellite%20internet%20services.%20It%20was%20a%20favorable%20outcome%20for%20Starlink%20and%20OneWeb%2C%20which%20told%20the%20country's%20telecom%20regulator%20they%20are%20against%20bidding%20for%20satellite%20airwaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatellite%20broadband%20services%20are%20%26quot%3Balso%20aligned%20to%20India's%20digital%20focus%26quot%3B%20and%20could%20enable%20better%20delivery%20of%20government%20programs%2C%20Nomura's%20Varma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EEasing%20Rules%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20in%20February%20eased%20foreign%20direct%20investment%20rules%20for%20the%20space%20sector%20allowing%20companies%20to%20invest%20in%20manufacturers%20of%20satellites%20and%20rockets%20without%20requiring%20government%20approvals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20will%20still%20need%20to%20resolve%20issues%20related%20to%20security%20approvals%2C%20spectrum%20allocation%20and%20pricing%20plans%20before%20it%20starts%20operating%20in%20India.%20Once%20it%20does%2C%20Mukesh%20Ambani-controlled%20Reliance%20Jio%20Infocomm%20Ltd.%20and%20Sunil%20Mittal-backed%20OneWeb%20will%20have%20trouble%20competing%2C%20according%20to%20Gareth%20Owen%2C%20a%20UK-based%20associate%20director%20at%20Counterpoint%20Research.%20OneWeb%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Eutelsat%20Communications%20SACA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SpaceX%20unit%20has%20more%20than%205%2C600%20active%20satellites%20in%20low-Earth%20orbit%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20launch%20tens%20of%20thousands%20more%2C%20as%20it%20aims%20to%20rival%20telecom%20providers%20that%20use%20larger%20and%20higher%20orbit%20satellites%20that%20hover%20over%20one%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarlink%20has%20a%20major%20advantage%2C%26quot%3B%20Owen%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20the%20largest%20constellation%20of%20LEO%20satellites%20deployed%20in%20orbit%2C%20covering%20most%20of%20the%20regions%2C%20and%20offering%20connectivity%20services%20across%20the%20globe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713584640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F945858cg_elon-musk-bloomberg_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felon-musks-india-trip-may-see-breakthroughs-for-starlink-tesla-5482135%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20Tesla%20Inc.'s%20largest-ever%20round%20of%20layoffs%20and%20hours%20before%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20will%20fly%20to%20India%20to%20squeeze%20in%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felon-musks-india-trip-may-see-breakthroughs-for-starlink-tesla-5482135%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felon-musks-india-trip-may-see-breakthroughs-for-starlink-tesla-5482135%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felon-musks-india-trip-may-see-breakthroughs-for-starlink-tesla-5482135%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Rio's%20Christ%20the%20Redeemer%20statue%20lit%20up%20green%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713583905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fimages%2Fic%2F640x360%2Fp0hs03p9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fprogrammes%2Fp0hs009d%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Christ%20the%20Redeemer%20statue%20in%20Rio%20turns%20green%20for