2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68852876.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Probable%20T20%20WC%20Squad%3A%20Race%20On%20For%20Back-up%20Opener%2C%203rd%20Spinner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20finalised%20by%20the%20end%20of%20April%20in%20order%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20ICC's%20May%201%20cut-off%20date%20for%20the%20provisional%20roster.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%2C%20Rishabh%20Pant%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20and%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20are%20certainties%20in%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20squad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%20five%20slots%20will%20be%20finalised%20based%20on%20the%20player's%20IPL%202024%20performance%20in%20the%20first%20four%20weeks%20of%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20tournament.%20A%20BCCI%20source%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20the%20national%20selection%20committee%20is%20unlikely%20to%20include%20any%20new%20player%20for%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20would%20not%20be%20any%20experimentation%20or%20left-field%20selections.%20All%20those%20who%20have%20played%20for%20India%20and%20have%20done%20well%20consistently%20in%20T20%20Internationals%20and%20the%20IPL%20will%20be%20rewarded%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BCCI%20official%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20to%20the%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20reported%20that%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20former%20skipper%20Virat%20Kohli%20could%20open%20for%20India%20at%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20West%20Indies%20and%20the%20United%20States%20starting%20from%20June%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20IPL%202024%20already%20witnessing%20some%20impressive%20individual%20performances%20from%20Indian%20players%2C%20fans%20and%20experts%20are%20still%20debating%20on%20the%20back-up%20opener%2C%20second-choice%20wicketkeeper%2C%20one%20finisher%20slot%20in%20the%20middle-order%20and%20the%20back-up%20spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20marquee%20ICC%20tournament%20fast%20approaching%2C%20we%20pick%20the%20remaining%20five%20slots%20from%20the%2010%20contenders%20to%20select%20the%20final%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShubman%20Gill%20vs%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20two%20young%20cricketers%20are%20expected%20to%20compete%20for%20the%20back-up%20opener's%20slot.%20While%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20are%20the%20automatic%20selections%2C%20Shubman%20Gill%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20preferred%20over%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20on%20his%20current%20form.%20GT%20captain%20Gill%20has%20been%20in%20good%20form%20in%20IPL%202024%2C%20having%20scored%20263%20runs%20in%20seven%20matches%2C%20including%20two%20fifties.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20RR%20opener%20Jaiswal%20has%20struggled%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20tournament%20with%20just%20121%20runs%20in%20seven%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%20choice%20wicket-keeper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20his%20brilliant%20comeback%20in%20the%20IPL%20following%20a%20near-fatal%20car%20crash%2C%20DC%20captain%20Rishabh%20Pant%20has%20almost%20sealed%20his%20place%20as%20first-choice%20wicket-keeper%20at%20the%20upcoming%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Meanwhile%2C%20India%20is%20expected%20to%20pick%20another%20wicket-keeper%20in%20the%2015-member%20squad.%20Sanju%20Samson%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20are%20the%20contenders%20to%20be%20the%20second-choice%20wicket-keeper.%20However%2C%20Sanju%20has%20been%20in%20better%20form%20than%20Rahul%20in%20IPL%202024%20so%20far.%20While%20Sanju%20has%20amassed%20276%20runs%20in%20seven%20matches%2C%20Rahul%20has%20204%20runs.%20Based%20on%20the%20current%20form%2C%20Sanju%20could%20be%20picked%20in%20the%20final%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERinku%20Singh%20vs%20Shivam%20Dube%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20the%20national%20selection%20committee%20opts%20to%20go%20with%20Virat%20and%20Rohit%20as%20openers%2C%20and%20Jaiswal%20and%20Gill%20are%20also%20included%2C%20one%20among%20Rinku%20Singh%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20could%20miss%20out%20from%20India's%2015-member%20squad.%C2%A0As%20finishers%20they%20are%20capable%20of%20add%20much-needed%20firepower%20down%20the%20order.%20Rinku%20and%20Shivam%20have%20been%20in%20great%20form%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20and%20their%20respective%20franchises%20in%20the%20IPL.%20While%20CSK's%20Shivam%20has%20hogged%20the%20limelight%2C%20having%20scored%20242%20runs%20in%20IPL%202024%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20160%2C%20KKR's%20star%20finisher%20Rinku%20has%20scored%2083%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20162.74%20and%20has%20looked%20in%20great%20touch%20with%20the%20bat%20in%20his%20limited%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%20vs%20Axar%20Patel%20vs%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnOne%20of%20the%20three%20will%20be%20selected%20as%20the%20third-choice%20spinner%20with%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20being%20certainties.%20Either%2C%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20or%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20could%20bring%20in%20variety%20as%20the%20only%20leg-spinner%20in%20the%20squad.%20However%2C%20Chahal%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20preferred%20choice%20over%20Bishnoi%20on%20current%20form.%20The%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20leg-spinner%20has%20found%20his%20mojo%20and%20is%20the%20second-highest%20wicket-taker%20in%20IPL%202024%20with%2012%20wickets%20in%20seven%20matches.%20LSG's%20Ravi%20Bishnoi%20has%20picked%20just%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20tournament%20so%20far.%20With%20Jadeja%20in%20the%20squad%2C%20Axar's%20inclusion%20looks%20bleak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArshdeep%20Singh%20-%20Avesh%20Khan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2