22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109448334.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAthiya%20Shetty%20cheers%20for%20KL%20Rahul%20as%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants%20win%20IPL%20match.%20KL%20Rahul%20hits%20half-century.%20Athiya%20shares%20match%20highlights%2C%20unseen%20pictures.%20Pregnancy%20rumors%20denied.%20They%20wed%20on%20January%2023%2C%202023%2C%20at%20Khandala%20farmhouse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Argentina%20President's%20%26quot%3BChainsaw%26quot%3B%20Threatens%20Oscar-Winning%20Cinema%2C%20Culture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPresident%20Javier%20Milei's%20%26quot%3Bchainsaw%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20budget%20cuts%20have%20not%20only%20caused%20deep%20financial%20pain%20to%20many%20Argentines%2C%20but%20is%20also%20threatening%20the%20country's%20Oscar-winning%20culture%20scene%2C%20industry%20players%20say.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20home%20and%20abroad%2C%20actors%2C%20directors%20and%20musicians%20accuse%20the%20self-declared%20%26quot%3Banarcho-capitalist%26quot%3B%20leader%20of%20showing%20disdain%20towards%20their%20industry%20as%20he%20slashes%20funding%20and%20rails%20against%20those%20who%20question%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilei%20himself%20has%20said%20the%20government%20must%20choose%20between%20%26quot%3Bfunding%20movies%20that%20nobody%20watches%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfeeding%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20denounced%20at%20least%20one%20artist%20criticizing%20his%20funding%20cuts%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bparasite%26quot%3B%20living%20off%20taxpayer%20money%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20hungry%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cultural%20industry%20in%20Argentina%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20tango%2C%20is%20responsible%20for%20some%20300%2C000%20formal%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20under%20Milei%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20are%20dismantling%20everything%20related%20to%20culture%20in%20general%20and%20cinema%20in%20particular%2C%26quot%3B%20award-winning%20Argentine%20actress%20Cecilia%20Roth%2C%20who%20has%20played%20in%20several%20movies%20by%20Spain's%20Pedro%20Almodovar%2C%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mexico%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20losses%20in%20direct%20state%20support%2C%20the%20industry%20is%20also%20reeling%20from%20the%20average%20Argentine%20having%20much%20less%20money%20to%20spend%20on%20such%20luxuries%20as%20films%20or%20plays%20as%20disposable%20income%20has%20shrunk%20and%20poverty%20levels%20have%20risen%20to%2060%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E-%20'Little%20hope'%20-%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArgentina's%20Incaa%20film%20institute%20has%20dismissed%20170%20of%20its%20645%20employees%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20suspended%20overtime%20payments%20and%20is%20not%20accepting%20any%20new%20projects%20for%20a%20period%20of%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncaa%20is%20financed%20mainly%20by%20taxes%20on%20ticket%20sales%20and%2025%20percent%20of%20the%20revenues%20of%20the%20National%20Communications%20Agency%20which%20co-finances%20dozens%20of%20films%20every%20year%2C%20including%20eight%20Oscar%20nominees%20and%20two%20winners%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Official%20Story%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20secret%20in%20their%20eyes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%20the%20panorama%20is%20darker%2C%26quot%3B%20Argentine%20production%20and%20audiovisual%20director%20Paula%20Orlando%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20considering%20leaving%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%2031-year-old%2C%20who%20has%2012%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20little%20hope.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E-%20'Strong%20bias'%20-%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoices%20of%20concern%20have%20also%20been%20raised%20abroad%2C%20from%20directors%20such%20as%20Almodovar%20himself%2C%20and%20Finland's%20Aki%20Kaurismaki.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Belgian%20film-making%20siblings%20Jean-Pierre%20and%20Luc%20Dardenne%2C%20France's%20Claire%20Denis%20and%20American%20Viggo%20Mortensen%20penned%20an%20article%20in%20which%20they%20said%20Argentina's%20cinema%20industry%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20brink.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusic%20and%20literature%2C%20too%2C%20have%20suffered%20the%20effects%20of%20Milei's%20cost-cutting%20measures%2C%20including%20the%20repeal%20of%20a%20law%20protecting%20independent%20book%20stores%20from%20being%20undercut%20by%20large%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20actions%20go%20to%20show%20that%20Milei%20and%20his%20government%20carry%20%26quot%3Ba%20strong%20bias%20against%20cultural%20industries%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Martin%20Gremmelspacher%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Argentine%20Book%20Chamber.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBook%20sales%2C%20he%20said%2C%20fell%2030%20percent%20in%20both%20January%20and%20February%20from%20a%20year%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E-%20'Dangerous'%20future%20-%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuis%20Sanjurjo%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20cultural%20policies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20said%20it%20was%20wrong%20to%20think%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20market%20can%20replace%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20no%20serious%20capitalist%20country%20in%20the%20world%20is%20there%20an%20absence%20of%20the%20state%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20development%20of%20culture%2C%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjurjo%20formerly%20headed%20an%20arts%20and%20culture%20industry%20sub-division%20in%20the%20now-defunct%20culture%20ministry%2C%20scrapped%20by%20Milei.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20appeared%20the%20ultra-liberal%20Milei%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Bbitter%26quot%3B%20towards%20the%20industry%20amid%20the%20global%20culture%20wars%20increasingly%20pitting%20people%20against%20each%20other%20on%20issues%20such%20as%20gay%20rights%2C%20abortion%2C