2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fpriscilla-queen-of-the-desert-2-original-cast-1235976995%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Man%20Jailed%20For%20Selling%20Controlled%20Substance%20On%20Dark%20Web%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2040-year-old%20Indian%20national%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20selling%20controlled%20substances%20on%20dark%20web%20marketplaces%20and%20ordered%20to%20forfeit%20approximately%20USD%20150%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanmeet%20Singh%2C%20of%20Haldwani%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20April%202019%20in%20London%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20extradited%20to%20the%20US%20in%20March%202023.%20In%20January%2C%20he%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20conspiracy%20to%20possess%20with%20intent%20to%20distribute%20controlled%20substances%20and%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20court%20documents%20and%20in%20statements%20made%20in%20court%2C%20Banmeet%20created%20vendor%20marketing%20sites%20on%20dark%20web%20marketplaces%2C%20such%20as%20Silk%20Road%2C%20Alpha%20Bay%2C%20Hansa%2C%20and%20others%2C%20to%20sell%20controlled%20substances%2C%20including%20fentanyl%2C%20LSD%2C%20ecstasy%2C%20Xanax%2C%20ketamine%2C%20and%20tramadol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECustomers%20paid%20with%20cryptocurrency%20for%20drugs%20ordered%20from%20Singh%20using%20the%20vendor%20sites.%20Singh%20then%20personally%20shipped%20or%20arranged%20the%20shipment%20of%20the%20drugs%20from%20Europe%20to%20the%20United%20States%20through%20US%20mail%20or%20other%20shipping%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%202012%20through%20July%202017%2C%20Singh%20controlled%20at%20least%20eight%20distribution%20cells%20within%20the%20US%2C%20including%20cells%20located%20in%20Ohio%2C%20Florida%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20Maryland%2C%20New%20York%2C%20North%20Dakota%2C%20and%20Washington%2C%20among%20other%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndividuals%20in%20these%20distribution