g%2C%20Bove%20complained%20of%20the%20DA's%20plans%20to%20the%20trial%20judge%2C%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Juan%20Merchan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBove%20said%20that%20the%20verdicts%2C%20judgments%2C%20and%20contempt-of-court%20orders%20that%20prosecutors%20want%20to%20question%20Trump%20about%20are%20mostly%20under%20appeal%20and%20%26quot%3Bunduly%20prejudicial%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20they'd%20unfairly%20prejudice%20the%20jury%20against%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20lawyer%20fought%20especially%20hard%20against%20jurors%20hearing%20that%20a%20federal%20jury%20in%20Manhattan%20had%20found%20Trump%20liable%20for%20violating%20Carroll%20with%20his%20hands%20during%20an%20assault%20in%20the%20mid-1990s%20%E2%80%94%20an%20attack%20that%20the%20judge%20said%20effectively%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-rape-e-jean-carroll-sexual-abuse-jury-judge-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20amounted%20to%20rape.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20the%20theory%20of%20this%20trial%3F%26quot%3B%20Bove%20asked%20angrily.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20they%20making%20arguments%20about%20sexual%20misconduct%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20demanded.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20case%20about%20documents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20lying%20about%20sexual%20assault%20%26quot%3Bis%20critical%20evidence%20that%20the%20jury%20should%20have%20in%20assessing%20his%20credibility%20if%20he%20testifies%2C%26quot%3B%20countered%20Matthew%20Colangelo%2C%20a%20prosecutor%20for%20District%20Attorney%20Alvin%20Bragg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMerchan%20said%20he%20would%20render%20a%20Sandoval%20decision%20Monday%2C%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20opening%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20will%20then%20call%20their%20first%20witness%2C%20a%20person%20whose%20name%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20made%20public.%20Their%20testimony%20will%20not%20be%20finished%20before%20the%20day%20breaks%20early%20for%20the%20fi