n%3EPassive%20income%20usually%20requires%20some%20upfront%20work%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20it%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Melissa%20Jean-Baptiste%20is%20not%20pictured.%3Cp%3EMaskot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20passive%20income%20stream%20can%20be%20a%20great%20way%20to%20generate%20extra%20money%20to%20pay%20down%20debt%20or%20save.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMelissa%20Jean-Baptiste%20learned%20first-hand%20that%20passive%20income%20is%20not%20that%20%26quot%3Bpassive%2C%26quot%3B%20especially%20in%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20maximize%20your%20chances%20of%20success%2C%20she%20recommends%20finding%20a%20side%20hustle%20that%20uses%20skills%20you%20already%20have.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-ways-to-earn-passive-income%5C%22%3EPassive%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20seems%20like%20a%20financial%20dream%20come%20true.%20The%20ability%20to%20make%20money%20in%20your%20sleep%20and%20have%20multiple%20streams%20of%20income%20with%20little%20effort%20is%20definitely%20money%20goals%2C%20especially%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-inflation%5C%22%3Einflation%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20making%20everyday%20life%20more%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Bpassive%20income%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20misnomer.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmillennialindebt.com%2Fabout%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMelissa%20Jean-Baptiste%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20used%20a%20side%20hustle%20selling%20lesson%20plans%20to%20help%20pay%20off%20%24100%2C000%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-private-student-loans%5C%22%3Estudent%20loan%3C%2Fa%3E%20debt%2C%20there%20is%20a%20catch.%20%26quot%3BThere%20tends%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20initial%20investment%20on%20your%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20writes%20in%20her%20book%2C%20%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSo%20%E2%80%A6%20This%20Is%20Why%20I'm%20Broke.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJean-Baptiste%20learned%20for%20herself%20that%20%26quot%3Bcreating%20a%20stream%20of%20passive%20income%20is%20hardly%20ever%20simple%20or%20passive.%26quot%3B%20She%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20passive%20income%20suggestions%20is%20to%20start%20a%20blog%20or%20create%20a%20digital%20product.%20But%20honestly%2C%20it%20is%20not%20as%20easy%20as%20YouTubers%20and%20social%20media%20influencers%20make%20it%20seem.%20There%20are%20many%20active%20foundational%20steps%20that%20must%20occur%20first%20before%20you%20are%20generating%20significant%20passive%20income%20from%20a%20blog%2C%20digital%20product%2C%20or%20rental%20property.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20generate%20passive%20income%2C%20and%20how%20do%20you%20get%20started%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFind%20the%20right%20side%20hustle%20for%20you%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20everyone%20needs%20a%20side%20hustle%2C%20especially%20in%20today's%20economy.%20But%20how%20do%20you%20find%20the%20one%20that's%20right%20for%20you%3F%20The%20wrong%20place%20to%20start%20is%20side%20hustles%20lauded%20by%20internet%20or%20social%20media%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20leaning%20into%20the%20side%20hustle%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20take%20stock%20of%20the%20skills%20you%20already%20have%20and%20try%20to%20monetize%20them.%20During%20the%20time%20that%20Jean-Baptiste%20was%20a%20teacher%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20she%20created%20a%20side%20hustle%20selling%20her%20lesson%20plans%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJean-Baptiste%20writes%20in%20her%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BMany%20people%20think%20side-hustling%20requires%20new%20skills%20and%20it%20doesn't.%20Look%20at%20what%20you%20are%20already%20doing%20and%20expand%20that%20into%20a%20side%20hustle.%20At%20the%20height%20of%20my%20lesson%20plan-selling%20era%2C%20I%20had%20forty%20to%20sixty%20assets%20in%20my%20digital%20store%20and%20was%20making%20%2410%2C000%20to%20%2412%2C000%20a%20year.%20This%20allowed%20me%20to%20use%20my%20teacher%20check%20for%20expenses%20and%20saving%2C%20while%20the%20side-hustle%20money%20went%20to%20my%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20reason%20many%20side%20hustles%20fail%20is%20that%20they're%20outside%20your%20skill%20set%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20the%20startup%20phase%20more%20difficult.%20%26quot%3BYour%20side%20hustle%20will%20only%20thrive%20if%20it%20fits%20your%20skills%20and%20lifestyle%20criteria%2C%20%5Bso%5D%20look%20and%20see%20what%20you%20are%20already%20doing%20and%20start%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Jean-Baptiste%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDetermine%20your%20ROI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20seek%20to%20increase%20your%20income%20streams%2C%20ask%20yourself%3A%20What%20is%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Froi%5C%22%3Ereturn%20on%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Jean-Baptiste%20advises%2C%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you've%20taken%20the%20time%20to%20assess%20your%20skills%20and%20outline%20your%20criteria%2C%20you%20have%20to%20determine%20the%20impact.%20Map%20out%20what%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20side%20hustle%20will%20entail%20on%20every%20level%20and%20how%20it%20will%20impact%20your%20financial%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20Jean-Baptiste%20writes%2C%20%26quot%3Bdetermine%20the%20skill%20set%20required%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20what%20you%20are%20offering%2C%20how%20convenient%20will%20it%20be%20for%20you%20to%20do%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20monetary%20goal%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20reach%20with%20this%20side%20hustle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20passive%20income%20is%20often%20not%20100%25%20passive%2C%20at%20least%20at%20first%2C%20the%20value%20of%20a%20side%20hustle%20or%20an%20additional%20income%20stream%20is%20undeniable.%20Jean-Baptiste%20writes%2C%20%26