Fbest-riding-lawn-mower%23best-riding-lawn-mower-for-extra-large-lawns-toro-titan-60-3%5C%22%3Ebest%20riding%20lawn%20mowers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20beat%20out%20gas-powered%20riding%20lawn%20mowers%20for%20many%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20batteries%20can%20last%20up%20to%20two%20acres.%20It%20also%20helps%20that%20you%20can%20go%20up%20to%207%20mph%20on%20this%20mower%20for%20maximum%20efficiency.%20You'll%20mow%20medium%20and%20large%20yards%20in%20no%20time%20with%20a%20deck%20size%20of%2042-%20or%2048%20inches.%20This%20John%20Deere%20starts%20with%20the%20push%20of%20a%20button%2C%20followed%20by%20bringing%20the%20handles%20together%20and%20pushing%20them%20forward%20or%20backward.%20If%20you%20push%20the%20handles%20outward%20and%20to%20the%20side%2C%20the%20lawn%20mower%20locks%20in%20place.%20The%20zero-turn%20riding%20mower%20adjusts%20with%20a%20foot%20lever%C2%A0%20among%2011%20different%20blade%20positions%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20Deere%20Z370R%20Electric%20ZTrak%20Mower%20on%20grass%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661eea8a10c6b0cde5f02b35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20electric%2C%20zero-turn%20John%20Deere%20Z370R%20Electric%20ZTrak%20Mower%20is%20the%20best%20riding%20mower%2C%20overall%2C%20beating%20out%20gas-powered%20models.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Temblador%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%2C%20the%20John%20Deere%20Z370R%20Electric%20ZTrak%20Mower%20does%20not%20come%20with%20a%20battery%20charger%20of%20any%20kind.%20In%20fact%2C%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20is%20plug%20an%20extension%20cord%20into%20the%20side%20of%20the%20machine%2C%20and%20it%20starts%20charging%20immediately.%20Even%20more%20exciting%2C%20the%20battery%20is%20in%20a%20chamber%20that%20keeps%20out%20water%20and%20dirt%2C%20so%20you%20can%20actually%20clean%20the%20riding%20mower%20with%20a%20hose%20and%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20any%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20comfortable%20seat%20and%20a%20deck%20where%20you%20can%20extend%20your%20legs%2C%20this%20riding%20lawn%20mower%20has%20a%20USB%20port%20in%20the%20onboard%20storage%20container%20to%20charge%20your%20phone%20as%20you%20mow.%20I%20particularly%20like%20how%20the%20LED%20headlights%20along%20the%20front%20and%20the%20sides%20light%20up%20the%20path%2C%20as%20well%20as%20how%20this%20lawn%20mower%20requires%20little%20maintenance%3A%20you%20won't%20ever%20have%20to%20change%20engine%20oil%2C%20spark%20plugs%2C%20an%20air%20filter%2C%20or%20mower%20belt%20with%20the%20John%20Deere%20Z370R%20Electric%20ZTrak%20Mower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20small%20yards%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20small%20yards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sun%20Joe%20MJ401C-PRO%20electric%20lawn%20mower%20may%20not%20have%20the%20width%20to%20be%20a%20practical%20option%20for%20larger%20yards%2C%20but%20its%20compact%20design%20and%20battery%20power%20make%20it%20ideal%20for%20small%20or%20medium-sized%20ones.%20You%20can%20mow%20up%20to%20a%20quarter%20acre%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%20The%20relatively%20narrow%20width%20also%20makes%20it%20convenient%20to%20maneuver%20around%20tight%20landscaping%20elements%20like%20rocks%20or%20other%20obstacles%20that%20require%20more%20precision%20than%20a%20larger%20mower%20offers.%20%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20the%20Sun%20Joe%20for%20this%20list%20because%20I%20appreciate%20anything%20that%20improves%20operation%20safety%2C%20especially%20lawn%20mowers.%20This%20model%20requires%20you%20to%20press%20the%20safety%20lock%20button%20and%20simultaneously%20pull%20the%20%26quot%3Bon%26quot%3B%20trigger%20to%20power%20it%20up.%20It%20reduces%20the%20chance%20of%20you%20starting%20the%20mower%20unintentionally.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%2014-inch%20cutting%20width%2C%20this%20compact%20mower%20is%20also%20well-suited%20for%20those%20with%20limited%20storage%20space.%20It's%20also%20incredibly%20lightweight.%20At%20just%2023.1%20pounds%2C%20it's%20comfortable%20to%20use%20and%20makes%20its%20lack%20of%20a%20self-propelling%20mechanism%20less%20of%20an%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sun%20Joe%20MJ401C-PRO%20features%20three%20height%20settings%2C%20less%20than%20our%20other%20options.%20It%20has%20a%20rear%20discharge%20chute%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal%20as%20the%20clippings%20will%20likely%20hit%20your%20feet%20as%20you%20walk.%20We%20previously%20recommended%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_040119_best-electric-mowers-20%26h%3D50fbac58519fffdf9f320daad8feb448971adaddec12fd92dec48f7907516687%26postID%3D61b8efc7f2a36b1ac9f42307%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-electric-lawn-mower%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSun-Joe-MJ401E-PRO-Electric-Discharge%252Fdp%252FB01DTIC778%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eside%20chute%20version%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20is%20currently%20unavailable.%C2%A0%20It%20could%20be%20the%20perfect%20fit%20if%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20hassle-free%20mower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20chose%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20chose%20the%20best%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20extensive%20online%20research%20from%20expert%20sources%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthrivingyard.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThriving%20Yard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20own%20hands-on%20experience%20with%20various%20brands%2C%20we%20assembled%20this%20list%20of%20the%20best%20electric%20mowers%20you%20can%20buy.%20We%20also%20used%20our%20experience%20with%20large%20power%20tools%20to%20help%20evaluate%20battery%20life%2C%20runtimes%2C%20and%20power%20output.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20we%20did%20not%20test%20all%20the%20options%20we%20chose%2C%20we%20reviewed%20owner%20and%20operation%20manuals%2C%20watched%20online%20tutorials%2C%20and%20consulted%20with%20lawn%20care%20equipment%20expert%20to%20develop%20our%20categories%20For%20models%20we%20did%20test%2C%20we%20used%20them%20on%20a%20half-acre%20yard%20a%20few%20times%20to%20get%20a%20feel%20for%20the%20cutting%20capabilities%2C%20self%20propel%20features%2C%20deck%20size%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20also%20used%20a%20set%20of%20specific%20criteria%20to%20help%20us%20evaluate%20and%20compare%20potential%20options%20and%20what%20to%20look%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20Capacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20cordless%20options%2C%20we%20paid%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20Ah%20(amp%20hour)%20of%20the%20included%20battery.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20Ah%2C%20the%20more%20energy%20the%20battery%20can%20store%2C%20the%20higher%20power%20output%2C%20and%20the%20longer%20it%20will%20last.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECharging%20Time%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20recharge%20a%20depleted%20battery%20can%20seriously%20affect%20the%20convenience%20of%20a%20cordless%20mower.%20If%20your%20battery%20can%20be%20recharged%20quickly%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20get%20back%20to%20work%20soon%2C%20and%20there's%20less%20of%20a%20chance%20that%20you'll%20need%20to%20purchase%20a%20second%20battery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERuntime%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOverall%20runtime%20per%20battery%20charge%20is%20probably%20the%20most%20important%20metric%20to%20consider%20when%20evaluating%20cordless%20mowers%20%E2%80%94%20obviously%2C%20corded%20models%20will%20provide%20the%20longest.%20The%20longer%20the%20runtime%2C%20the%20better%2C%20especially%20for%20larger%20mowers%20that%20will%20be%20purchased%20to%20use%20on%20larger%20lawns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20lighter%20the%20mower%20weighs%2C%20the%20less%20effort%20it%20will%20place%20on%20the%20battery%20and%20the%20longer%20the%20overall%20runtime.%20We%20did%20our%20best%20to%20choose%20lighter%20options%20whenever%20possible%20while%20still%20considering%20overall%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EElectric%20lawn%20mower%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20benefits%20of%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20lawn%20mowers%20are%20just%20as%20effective%20as%20gas-powered%20lawn%20mowers%20but%20without%20certain%20drawbacks.%20They%20don't%20require%20gas%20or%20oil%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20emit%20harmful%20fumes%20or%20exhaust%2C%20making%20them%20far%20more%20environmentally%20friendly.%20Most%20importantly%2C%20electric%20lawnmowers%20come%20with%20far%20less%20maintenance.%20You'll%20never%20have%20to%20change%20a%20spark%20plug%20(because%20they're%20not%20outfitted%20with%20them)%20or%20remove%20the%20oil%20and%20gas%20before%20you%20winterize%20the%20mower%20in%20the%20winter.%20They%20are%20also%20quieter%20in%20operation.%20While%20they%20may%20have%20a%20more%20expensive%20up-front%20cost%2C%20they%20will%20also%20be%20cheaper%20to%20operate%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20do%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%20last%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBattery-powered%20mowers%20themselves%20can%20last%20up%20to%2010%20years%2C%20but%20their%20batteries%20will%20only%20last%20about%204%20years%20before%20they're%20unable%20to%20hold%20an%20effective%20charge.%20To%20ensure%20your%20batteries%20will%20last%20as%20long%20as%20possible%2C%20try%20to%20completely%20deplete%20the%20battery%20before%20recharging%20it.%20This%20will%20reduce%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20charging%20cycles%20placed%20on%20the%20battery%2C%20increasing%20its%20lifespan.%20You%20should%20also%20do%20your%20best%20to%20remove%20the%20battery%20from%20the%20charger%20once%20it's%20fully%20charged%3Cstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorded%20mowers%20have%20a%20similar%20lifespan%20as%20long%20as%20they're%20cared%20for%20properly.%20There%20are%20no%20batteries%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20but%20their%20extension%20cords%20are%20just%20as%20important%20to%20pay%20attention%20to.%20This%20means%20using%20the%20correct%20gauge%20for%20the%20job%2C%20which%20indicates%20how%20thick%20the%20cord%20is.%20The%20thicker%20the%20cord%2C%20the%20more%20voltage%20will%20reach%20the%20mower%20and%20the%20less%20unnecessary%20work%20the%20motor%20has%20to%20do.%20Your%20mower's%20operating%20manual%20should%20tell%20you%20the%20best%20gauge%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20expensive%20are%20electric%20lawn%20mowers%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EElectric%20lawn%20mowers%20are%20available%20at%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20prices%2C%20although%20corded%20models%20tend%20to%20be%20cheaper%20than%20battery-powered%20options.%20Corded%20mowers%20also%20won't%20require%20any%20additional%20battery%20purchases%20over%20time.%20Size%20also%20plays%20a%20part.%20Large%20riding%20mowers%20can%20cost%20thousands%20of%20dollars%2C%20while%20smaller%2C%20compact%20machines%2C%20like%20the%20Sun%20Joe%20MJ401C-PRO%2C%20our%20recommendation%20for%20small%20yards%2C%20can%20be%20found%20for%20about%20%24200.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20requires%20the%20fuel%20or%20oil%20that%20gas-powered%20models%20do%2C%20which%20should%20cut%20down%20on%20the%20overall%20expense%20of%20the%20mower.%20However%2C%20the%20long-term%20cost%20of%20replacement%20batteries%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20cost%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20%E2%80%94%20should%20be%20considered%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20it%20safe%20to%20cut%20wet%20grass%20with%20an%20electric%20mower%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ego%20mower%20manual%2C%20you%20should%20avoid%20cutting%20wet%20grass%20with%20your%20electric%20mower%20for%20two%20reasons.%20First%2C%20the%20moisture%20can%20affect%20the%20electrical%20components%20of%20the%20mower%20and%20cause%20serious%20damage%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20warranty.%20Secondly%2C%20using%20your%20mower%20on%20wet%20grass%20is%20a%20potential%20safety%20hazard%20and%20can%20cause%20you%20to%20slip%20or%20fall%20and%20potentially%20injure%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWet%20grass%20can%20also%20present%20maintenance%20and%20cleaning%20challenges.%20It%20can%20become%20stuck%20on%20the%20deck%20and%20other%20components%2C%20and%20unlike%20gas-powered%20mowers%2C%20you%20can't%20just%20spray%20it%20off%20with%20a%20hose.%20As%20long%20as%20you%20stick%20to%20cutting%20dry%20grass%2C%20you'll%20have%20a%20much%20easier%20time%20cleaning%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20you%20leave%20an%20electric%20lawn%20mower%20outside%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20electrical%20components%20and%20vulnerable%20batteries%2C%20we%20don't%20recommend%20leaving%20your%20mower%20outdoors%20when%20it's%20not%20in%20use.%20Both%20Ego%20and%20Greenworks%20recommend%20keeping%20their%20electric%20mowers%20indoors%20in%20a%20cool%2C%20dry%20space.%20They%20also%20state%20that%20you%20should%20never%20cover%20them%20with%20a%20plastic%20tarp%2C%20which%20can%20trap%20moisture%20that%20can%20damage%20the%20internal%20components.%20If%20you%20need%20to%20keep%20your%20mower%20outside%2C%20keep%20it%20elevated%20and%20off%20the%20ground.%20This%20will%20allow%20air%20to%20flow%20around%20it%20and%20prevent%20unnecessary%20moisture%20damage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20electric%20lawn%20mower%20overall%3A%20Ego%20LM2102SP%2021-inch%20Self-Propelled%20Lawn%20Mower%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22person%20pushing%20white%20and%20black%20Ego%20Power%2B%20LM2102SP%20to%20cut%20tall%20grass%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F614107792db0850019a9752d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EEgo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2