Research%20Projects%20Agency%20showed%20the%20jets%20maneuvering%20through%20the%20skies%20around%20one%20another%20in%20a%20step%20up%20from%20previous%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI-controlled%20fighter%20jet%2C%20called%20the%20X-62A%20Variable%20Stability%20In-flight%20Simulator%20Test%20Aircraft%2C%20is%20a%20modified%20version%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ff-16-fighter-jets-russia-ukraine-war-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF-16%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECol.%20James%20Valpiani%2C%20commandant%20of%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20Test%20Pilot%20School%2C%20said%20the%20AI%20agents%20in%20the%20aircraft%20were%20able%20to%20be%20upgraded%20or%20switched%20out%20between%20missions%2C%20potentially%20complicating%20air%20warfare%20for%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20able%20to%20generate%20changes%20to%20software%20overnight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20were%20able%20to%20upload%20the%20software%20changes%20to%20the%20aircraft%20while%20it%20was%20holding%20short%2C%20ready%20to%20take%20off%20and%20even%20airborne.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20able%20to%20transition%20between%20multiple%20versions%20of%20the%20same%20AI%20agent%20airborne%2C%20between%20combat%20sets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FC8yjtaZfNCw%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22DARPA%20ACE%20%26amp%3B%20USAF%20X-62A%20Achieve%20World%20First%20for%20AI%20in%20Aerospace%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20X-62A%20has%20taken%20at%20least%2021%20test%20flights%20since%20it%20was%20built%20in%20December%