%98Ctrl%20%2B%20F%E2%80%99%20with%20trembling%20hands%2C%20confirming%20that%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20numb%20and%20confused%2C%20and%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20only%20me%3F%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20candid%20post%20that%20now%20has%20over%201.25%20lakh%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20came%20to%20the%20bureaucrat%E2%80%99s%20rescue%20that%20day.%20Jitin%20met%20his%20friend%20and%20received%20an%20important%20life%20lesson%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20everyone%20in%20a%20difficult%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20happens%2C%20happens%20for%20good%20only.%20We%20can%20only%20give%20our%20100%25.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%20one%20to%20be%20depressed%20and%20do%20nothing%2C%20other%20to%20immediately%20bounce%20back%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20and%20do%20what%20all%20past%20selected%20candidates%20have%20done%20who%20faced%20rejections%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20and%20author%20chose%20the%20second%20option%20and%20was%20selected%20in%20the%20next%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20necessary%20for%20everyone%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20same%20path%20as%20there%20are%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345398%2Ffree-upsc-coaching-mentorship-programme-delhi-former-irs-officer-ravi-kapoor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20options%20beyond%20UPSC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20such%20students%2C%20he%20advises%20taking%20a%20break%20and%20then%20figuring%20out%20a%20future%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetter%20things%20are%20waiting%20for%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20bureaucrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20entire%20post%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cd