worker-mothers-day-love-rescue%2F%5C%22%3Emother%E2%80%99s%20profession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Growing%20up%2C%20she%20was%20repeatedly%20told%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20daughter%20of%20a%20sex%20worker%20will%20become%20a%20sex%20worker%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20taught%20to%20hate%20my%20mother%20and%20my%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sandhya%20in%20a%20free-flowing%20interaction%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilaap.org%2Ffundraisers%2Fhelp-survivors-of-trafficking-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilaap.org%2Ffundraisers%2Fhelp-survivors-of-trafficking-1%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20class%2C%20she%20recalls%20breaking%20down%20and%20crying%20out%20a%20resounding%20%E2%80%9Cno%E2%80%9D%20that%20shook%20everyone%20present%20there.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20she%20spoke%20out%20about%20being%20raped%2C%20confiding%20in%20her%20mentor%2C%20Robin%20Chaurasiya.%20Sandhya%20recalls%20this%20moment%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20path-breaking%20ones%20in%20her%20life%20at%20the%20time%2C%20when%20she%20was%2018%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20happened%20thanks%20to%20the%20theatre%20class%20and%20therapy%20sessions%20conducted%20by%20%E2%80%98Kranti%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20an%20NGO%20that%20empowers%20children%20of%20sex%20workers%20to%20become%20agents%20of%20social%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti1-1713281048.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kranti%20provides%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20daughters%20of%20sex%20workers%5C%22