esearcher%20for%20shampoo%20fragrances.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20font%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20before%20going%20to%20college%2C%20I%20had%20to%20create%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%20on%20the%20computer.%20Since%20they%20wanted%20someone%20who%20could%20handle%20computers%20and%20had%20an%20artistic%20mind%2C%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20worked%20there%20for%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F346774%2Fbengaluru-residents-saving-water-scarcity-rainwater-harvesting-recycle-greywayer-aerators-restrictors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBengaluru%20resident.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hardika%20started%20Kinara%20Capital%20in%202011%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-1713159170-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347263%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHardika%20started%20Kinara%20Capital%20in%202011%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20managed%20her%20pocket%20money%2C%20raising%20funds%20for%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20the%20US%20was%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Hardika%20shares%20that%20she%20spent%20almost%2018%20months%20preparing%20for%20all%20the%20different%20exams%2C%20but%20mostly%20just%20trying%20to%20find%20avenues%20for%20her%20finances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20really%20not%20cheap%20to%20go%20to%20the%20US%20in%20the%2080s.%20Liberal%20arts%20colleges%20then%20gave%20some%20financial%20aid%2C%20but%20it%20was%20very%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20parents%20came%20to%20her%20rescue%20and%20sold%20their%20house%20to%20fund%20her%20education%2C%20moving%20to%20a%20smaller%20rented%20apartment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20teenager%20entered%20Knox%20College%20in%20Illinois%2C%20USA%2C%20where%20she%20pursued%20a%20BA%20in%20computer%20science.%20The%20degree%20gave%20her%20the%20opportunity%20to%20study%20everything%20from%20world%20history%2C%20anthropology%2C%20economics%20to%20symbolic%20logic%20apart%20from%20traditional%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20she%20worked%20at%20Accenture%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20then%20back%20again%20in%20the%20US%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20financial%20services%2C%20technology%20and%20consulting%20for%20almost%2019%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20also%20brought%20her%20to%20India%20almost%2010%20years%20later%2C%20in%20the%20post%20liberalisation%20era.%20For%20someone%20working%20in%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20she%20found%20a%20stark%20difference%20and%20a%20big%20gap%20in%20accessibility%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20filled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20decided%20to%20spend%20her%20weekends%20every%20summer%20as%20a%20social%20impact%20business%20mentor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20spend%20time%20with%20entrepreneurs%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20India%2C%20and%20help%20them%20develop%20their%20business%20ideas%2C%20models%20and%20also%20face%20related%20challenges%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20followed%20this%20mentorship%20up%20with%20an%20executive%20MBA%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20Haas%20School%20of%20Business.%20She%20noticed%20a%20pattern%20in%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20people%20in%20India%2C%20and%20one%20recurring%20challenge%20emerged%20%E2%80%94%20access%20to%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20missing%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20spent%20three%20months%20in%20India%20with%20bankers%2C%20techies%2C%20and%20self-help%20groups%20to%20understand%20where%20the%20gap%20in%20access%20to%20capital%20lay%20before%20starting%20Kinara.%20After%20all%2C%20micro%20finance%20and%20Non-Banking%20Financial%20Companies%20(NBFCs)%20had%20expanded%20very%20well%20in%20the%20country%20by%20then%2C%20and%20were%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20people%20in%20rural%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Hardika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinara%20Capital%20has%20disbursed%20over%201.2%20lakh%20loans%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-5-1713159172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKinara%20Capital%20has%20disbursed%20over%201.2%20lakh%20loans%20so%20far%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20major%20credit%20gap%2C%20the%20consultant%20found%2C%20was%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98missing%20middle%E2%80%99%2C%20of%20people%20in%20need%20of%20loans%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeeting%20these%20small%20business%20owners%2C%20SHGs%2C%20women%20entrepreneurs%2C%20led%20to%20a%20deja%20vu%20moment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDidn%E2%80%99t%20her%20mother%20face%20the%20same%20problem%2025%20years%20back%3F%20Why%20was%20no%20one%20able%20to%20fix%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325587%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-runs-lending-platform-for-rural-indian-women-loans-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecredit%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20this%20income%20group%2C%20wondered%20Hardika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20should%20have%20unfulfilled%20dreams%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20capital%20like%20her%20mother%2C%20the%2053-year-old%20decided%20to%20solve%20the%20problem.%20Providing%20collateral%20was%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20this%20bracket%2C%20which%20she%20solved%20through%20Kinara%20Capital%20by%20providing%20unsecured%20loans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20gap%20across%20tier%201%2C%202%20and%203%20cities%20was%20unsecured%20business%20lending%2C%20as%20most%20of%20the%20borrowers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20land%20or%20property%20to%20offer%20as%20collateral.%20I%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20people%20in%20these%20cities%20who%20are%20on%20the%20fringe%20of%20inclusion%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20sets%20Kinara%20Capital%20apart%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Kinara%20Capital%E2%80%99s%20launch%20in%202011%2C%20Hardika%20raised%20funds%20from%20social%20impact%20investment%20funds%20like%20Michael%20%26amp%3B%20Susan%20Dell%20Foundation%2C%20Patamar%20Capital%2C%20Gaja%20Capital%2C%20British%20International%20Investment%20(BII)%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kinara%20Capital%20runs%20HerVikas%20to%20help%20women%20entreprenuers%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fhardika-4-1713159175-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347265%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKinara%20Capital%20runs%20HerVikas%20to%20help%20women%20entreprenuers%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKinara%20vets%20its%20customers%20with%20the%20help%20of%20AI%20and%20Machine%20learning%2C%20with%20the%20last%20mile%20delivery%20done%20by%20its%20officers.%20They%20have%20133%20branches%20across%20100%20cities%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20have%20disbursed%20over%201%2C25%2C000%20loans%20so%20far%2C%20with%20assets%20under%20management%20of%20over%20Rs%203%2C170%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interest%20rates%20range%20from%2020%20to%2032%20percent%20on%20a%20reducing%20balance%20basis%2C%20with%20the%20average%20tenure%20ranging%20from%2036%20to%2038%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20underwriting%20is%2095%20percent%20digital%20and%205%20percent%20physical%2C%20through%20our%20sales%20officers%20on%20ground.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20blended%20tech%20model%20with%20a%20physical%20branch%20network%20where%20most%20of%20the%20underwriting%20and%20collections%20are%20done%20online%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20social%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%2020%20percent%20of%20their%20monthly%20disbursements%20go%20to%20existing%20customers%2C%20helping%20them%20grow%20their%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20clients%2C%20Divya%20explains%20how%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20policy%20helped%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20runs%20a%20company%20called%20Brookwoods%20Technologies%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20and%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20loan%20for%20her%20business.%20Since%20her%20business%20was%20less%20than%20a%20year%20old%2C%20most%20lenders%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20NBFCs%20and%20banks%20lend%20after%20a%20business%20completes%20three%20years%20of%20operations.%20Kinara%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20such%20conditions%20and%20gave%20us%20a%20loan%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20immensely.%20The%20entire%20process%20was%20streamlined%20and%20online.%20An%20officer%20from%20their%20team%20came%20for%20inspection%20and%20sanctioned%20the%20loan%20very%20quickly%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDivya%20has%20been%20able%20to%20grow%20her%20company%20to%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20crores%20in%203%20years.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20all%20this%2C%20Hardika%20states%20that%20Kinara%20is%20profitable%20today%20and%20rearing%20to%20reach%20more%20business%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20Kinara%E2%80%99s%20existence%20began%20thanks%20to%20a%20woman%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20hence%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20their%20HerVikas%20programme%2C%20which%20offers%20discounts%20to%20women%20entrepreneurs%20to%20boost%20their%20businesses%2C%20remains%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20disbursed%20Rs%20700%20crores%20in%20the%20past%205%20years%2C%20offering%20a%201%20percent%20interest%20discount%2C%2060%20day%20repayment%20holiday%2C%2050%20reduction%20in%20processing%20fees.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%203.5%20percent%20to%204%20percent%20Non-Performing%20Asset%20(NPA)%20rate%2C%20Hardika%20wants%20to%20reach%20more%20MSMEs%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%20hoping%20to%20reach%202%20lakh%20additional%20customers%20in%20the%20next%203%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20notion%20that%20unsecured%20business%20lending%20is%20risky%20and%20customers%20will%20disappear%20with%20your%20money.%20Our%20numbers%20prove%20that%20this%20is%20so%20far%20away%20from%20the%20truth.%20Customers%20are%20grateful%20to%20have%20access%20to%20capital%20and%20repay%20on%20time.%20They%20also%20use%20the%20money%20judiciously%20to%20grow%20their%20businesses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20enhance%20more%20jobs%20by%20reaching%20more%20small%20businesses.%20She%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20any%20business%20owner%20with%20potential%20to%20lose%20out%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20could%20have%20been%20a%20big%20franchise%20owner%20had%20Kinara%20been%20present%20then.%20Let%20no%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20lose%20out%20on%20their%20potential%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20capital.%20Let%20there%20be%20no%20regrets%2C%20ifs%20and%20buts%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hardika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%2